Don't even get me started.

832
00:50:04,400 --> 00:50:07,200
Forgive me, but I still don't understand
how that justifies...

833
00:50:07,300 --> 00:50:09,200
Let me tell you something, brother -

834
00:50:09,200 --> 00:50:12,300
I don't know how they do it
out in Roland Park.

835
00:50:12,300 --> 00:50:16,500
Maybe Prosecutor Obonda
can enlighten me on that.

836
00:50:16,500 --> 00:50:21,000
But my world is strictly cash-and-carry,
and I am Clay Davis -

837
00:50:21,000 --> 00:50:24,100
my people need something,
they know where to find me.

838
00:50:25,000 --> 00:50:28,100
Let me tell you, brother,
I step out the door,

839
00:50:28,100 --> 00:50:30,500
hit the corner of Mosher
and Pennsylvania,

840
00:50:30,500 --> 00:50:32,700
