848
00:50:55,200 --> 00:51:00,300
Yeah, but you give me 20,000 for a basketball
and an air pump,

849
00:51:00,300 --> 00:51:04,700
I am pullin' goodly on that
for whatever, whoever comes at me.

850
00:51:04,800 --> 00:51:09,400
"Senator Clay,
I gots to bury my mother,

851
00:51:09,400 --> 00:51:11,100
