I ain't gonna lie to you.

864
00:51:51,100 --> 00:51:53,500
I'm gonna do
the same damn thing tomorrow,

865
00:51:53,500 --> 00:51:56,500
and the day after that
and the day after that,

866
00:51:56,500 --> 00:51:59,500
